<%= render "shared/banner", title: "Projects", details: "We are an established, innovative energy and sustainability consultancy that provide a full suite of modelling and compliance solutions across all sectors of the property and construction industry. We easily integrate into your design team and are experienced in providing solutions that are tailored to your projects specific requirements from planning to project completion. Below is a sample of the projects we have worked in various sectors, from Residential and Hospitality to Healthcare, Commercial and University", sub: nil, url: 'proj-bg.webp' %>
